<title>USA: Engineering Animation names financial officer.</title>
<headline>Engineering Animation names financial officer.</headline>
<dateline>AMES, Iowa 1997-08-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Engineering Animation Inc said Monday that Jerome Behar has been named vice president of finance and chief financial officer</p>
<p>Behar succeeds Michael Jewell, who is leaving EAI to manage a family business in Seattle.</p>
<p>In another development, Adrian Sannier has been promoted to vice president and general manager of EAI's interactive and custom animation business units, a new position.</p>
<p>EAI provides 3D visualization technology for education and entertainment needs.</p>
<p>			((Chicago newsdesk 312 408 8787))</p>
